    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to    <strong>l i m e n t i o n a l</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179000/extras/0f42b20302fd3ad24cdb2733016e185b.avif?t=1762026500\" width=1560 height=870 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>l i m e n t i o n a l   </strong>is a first-person platforming and parkour game with horror elements, and some emphasis on mental health. Traverse and explore the environments to dive deeper and unlock secrets, and collect elusive MAXIMS. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179000/extras/18e6d564563606b6ea69ec2d247c6b27.avif?t=1762026500\" width=1560 height=862 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore</strong> liminal and surreal spaces, traversing puzzles to succeed as you become increasingly entrapped in the world and your mind.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Record</strong>   your findings using your Camera, capturing the essence of the strange world you find yourself in. The camera will also reveal things hidden, and help fend off what lies in wait ...  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179000/extras/d2ac3f8020feea375b3b44e22b919aaf.avif?t=1762026500\" width=1312 height=810 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive</strong>  the relentless mazes and traps of this otherworld, and the horrors that lie within.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
